[This is truly a travesty when an effective vaccine is available. It is nonsensical that a governor can override a public health need.

"COVID-related child deaths in Florida more than doubled in just over a month, according to data from the Florida Department of Health.

"A Florida Department of Health weekly report showed 7 children under the age of 16 died from coronavirus complications from the start of the pandemic to 30 Jul 2021, a 15-month period. Per the department's latest report from 3 Sep 2021, the number has jumped to 17 deaths since 30 Jul 2021.

"Though the American Academy of Pediatrics (AAP) Florida chapter said most of these deaths were aligned with underlying health conditions, this sharp climb has pediatric experts worried and uncertain about the COVID delta variant in the coming months."

GOP governors like Florida's Ron Desantis continue to fight individual school districts over mask mandates in school settings. A judge ruled in August [2021] that Desantis could not issue a mask ban, which was upheld in a court decision on Wednesday [8 Sep 2021], allowing school districts to continue imposing a mask mandate. However, the decision was overruled when an appeals court ruled in favor of the governor's ban on Friday [10 Sep 2021]. The US Department of Education opened a civil rights investigation into mask bans in 6 states, including Florida."
(https://www.businessinsider.com/covid-related-childhood-deaths-in-florida-double-in-a-month-2021-9)
- Mod.LK]

